author: dkulp
msg: [CXF-1140] For http urls to wsdl/schema, well cache the results as wsdl4j doesn't call "close()" till the end which results in the connection to the server being held open consuming ports on the server.   Caching allows the keepalives to work and everything transferred over one connection.
